channel.title: Client Error - Does not support silab items?
channel.description:
Do clients support silab items? I downloaded like two and they both do not support silab items. One one of them, the better one, when I log in im invisible. Then, when I go into the tab where the stuff you're wearing is and it dc's me and gives me this error:
Exception in thread "Thread-3" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 14086 at Class8.method198(Unknown Source) at Class8.method200(Unknown Source) at client.method105(Unknown Source) at client.method36(Unknown Source) at client.method102(Unknown Source) at client.method9(Unknown Source) at Applet_Sub1.run(Unknown Source) at client.run(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
Can someone please help with this problem?
